  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      C8 sciences program is a cognitive training program mainly developed for the students, and
      the effectiveness is well established. The aim of this trial is to assess clinical efficacy
      of the program for cognitive rehabilitation of the patients with stroke or brain injury.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
